title: Junior Bake Off UK S03E01-E05 HDTV.x264-TM
description:
Junior Bake Off is back for a brand-new 15-part series, hosted by Sam and Mark. Judges, top international chef Allegra McEvedy and executive pastry chef Graham Hornigold test 40 of Britain's best young bakers over a series of 10 heats followed by a knock-out week of finals. In each heat four bakers will face two challenges, the technical and the show-stopper, before one of them wins through to the next round.




Junior Bake Off - Series 3, Episodes 1 to 5



Original Air Dates: 02-Nov-2015 to 06-Nov-2015
